  schema={howtoSchema}
>
  <span slot="why-trust">
    <li>✅ <strong>5 methods tested</strong> across real patios, decks, and yards</li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Zero damage</strong> — all methods leave no holes or permanent marks</li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Hardware cost listed</strong> — no hidden expensive tools needed</li>
    <li>✅ <strong>Spanning power tested</strong> — long spans (50+ ft) to small balconies</li>
  </span>
</Article>
